data.description:
Show us your passion for biking and you have the chance to win a trip to hang out with Thule Crew member and freeriding mountain biker Chris Van Dine!

World famous freeriding mountain biker Chris Van Dine developed a taste for speed at an early age and won his first mountain bike race when he was eight. data.title: Wulong Mountain Quest 2013 - Thule Adventure Team
data.description: The Thule Adventure Team takes on the Wulong Mountain Quest, one of the most prestigious multisport races in the world. Watch as they fight through four tough days of mountain biking, trail running, kayaking, canyoning, caving and repelling.

asset.title: Wulong Mountain Quest 2013 - Thule Adventure Team
asset.description:
Watch Thule Adventure Team in Wulong Mountain Quest, one of the world's most prestigious multisport races. The race attracts the best adventure racing teams in the world, and the competition is fierce.

The members of Thule Adventure Team - Martin Flinta, Jacky Boisset, Myriam Guillot and Marcel Hagener - give all they have during four tough days of mountain biking, trail running, kayaking, canyoning, caving and repelling.


Professional filmmaker Sylvain Boisset followed the team during this stage race which took place in Wulong in southern China,  September 4-7, 2013. The breath-taking scenery and beautiful landscape make this race truly spectacular.

www.thule.com/thulecrew

data.title: How to Install the Thule Sprint 569 Fork Mount Bike Rack
data.description: This complete fork mount bike carrier offers maximum bike protection with wheel chock supports for increased rear wheel security and stability.

asset.title: Bike Carrier Roof - Thule Sprint 569
asset.description:
Thule Sprint 569 - the most complete fork mount bike carrier for maximum bike protection.
 
• Patented AcuTight clamping head “clicks” when optimal hold is reached controlling the torque going into the bike frame
• The recommended roof option for transportation of bikes with sensitive frames (e.g. carbon)
• Road Dampening Technology (RDT) elastomers are imbedded in the rack attachments to absorb road shock and vibrations
• Ratcheting wheel strap with RDT secures the rear wheel without damaging the rim
• Wheel chock supports for increased rear wheel security and stability
• Telescopic wheel tray for custom fit to bike and vehicle
• Lockable – bike to bike carrier, bike carrier to load carrier (locks included).
• T-track adapters (20x20mm) are included for mounting on Thule WingBar Edge/Thule AeroBlade Edge, Thule WingBar/Thule AeroBlade, Thule SlideBar, and Thule AeroBar.
• Fulfils the City Crash norm.

Learn more at www.thule.com
asset.author: ThuleBringYourLife

data.title: Features & Benefits of a Thule Excellence XT Cargo Carrier
data.description: This exclusive roof box provides tons of features including automatic load fixation: by just closing the box lid, the load will be fixated and secured.

asset.title: Roof box - Thule Excellence XT
asset.description:
Looking for an exclusive roof box for your car? Watch this video and learn about the features of Thule Excellence XT and how to install it on the roof of your car.

Thule Excellence XT

- Exclusive design with a unique 2-tone colour combination and advanced aerodynamics with diffuser technology to optimize air flow around box.
- Automatic load fixation: by just closing the box lid, the load will be fixated and secured automatically with the new integrated loading net and crash nose.
- Pre-installed Power-Click quick-mount system with integrated torque indicator for fast and secure fitting using one hand only.
- Dual-Side opening with outside lid handles for convenient mounting, loading and unloading.
- Central locking system provides maximum safety. The grip-friendly Thule Comfort key can only be removed if all locking points are securely closed.
- Designed for having a forwarded position on the car roof, enabling full access to the trunk without interference with the roofbox.
- Including Thule Box light. Automatic on/off function when opening or closing box lid.
- Including a custom-fit lid cover to protect the box from scratches and dust during storage.

Learn more at www.thule.com
asset.author: ThuleBringYourLife

data.title: Features & Benefits of Thule SnowPack Ski Carrier
data.tags: Thule SnowPack Ski Carrier, Snowboard Carrier, Snow Pack
data.description: This sleek, aerodynamic roof mounted ski carrier is designed to carry all types of skis and snowboards.

asset.title: Ski Carrier – Thule SnowPack
asset.description:
Thule SnowPack is a sleek, aerodynamic roof mounted ski carrier for all types of skis and snowboards.  Watch this video and learn how to install the carrier on top of your car. 

Thule SnowPack

• Rooftop carrier designed to carry all types of skis and snowboards. 
• Holds skis and snowboards securely with ultra-soft rubber arms that grip without scratching the surfaces. 
• Safely carries thicker modern skis and snowboards, and reduces the carrier height when unloaded thanks to the integrated vertical spring system. 
• Easy to open and close while wearing gloves via an oversized push button. 
• Added roof clearance for skis with tall bindings thanks to included extension feet that raise the carrier. 
• Lock the skis to the carrier, and the carrier to the car, with the Thule One-Key system (locks included). 
• Fits directly into the load bars’ T-tracks via the integrated, tool-free mounting hardware (square bar mounting kit available as an accessory). 
• Meets stringent safety standards (City Crash test and TÜV-approved).

Learn more at www.thule.com
